name: Lucid Wonderland
description:
An art piece inspired by the stars under the night sky. The night meant to be seen as the means of escape from reality burdened by the dominance of the day. The dominant red stars latching onto the abstract blue voice of freedom spreading its parasitic ideals conquering it, with the whole substance ending into points of submissive breakdowns. 

Format: MP4
Resolution: 1920 x 1080 (FHD)
